<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<Project Type="Project" LVVersion="24008000">
	<Property Name="NI.LV.All.SaveVersion" Type="Str">Editor version</Property>
	<Property Name="NI.LV.All.SourceOnly" Type="Bool">true</Property>
	<Property Name="NI.Project.Description" Type="Str">Use T-CLK to demonstrate:
3x generation channels across 2x FGEN modules connected to 3x acquisition channels across 2x scope modules 
o	demonstrate the generation and acquisition of a three-phase system using T-Clk to synchronize all four instruments to show that the three phases are being generated and acquired exactly 120deg out of phase with each other 

Also have another version of the code that's either synchronized manually (e.g. not using T-CLK) OR just software timed.</Property>
